posting_body: ['Say hello to your new home!', 'Tramor at Sunchase is a Perfect location for all of your needs!', 'Our property is quiet little area nestled behind Highway 79 on the east side.', 'Near all major highways, such as: I35, 45, 620, and Mopac.', "Perfectly located to satisfy your needs and amenities that will make you feel as if it's your own home!", '5 minutes from Kalahari resorts and Old Settlers park.', 'Call us today to check out our beautiful property and see what Sunchase has to offer!', 'RENTAL FEATURES:', '+ Newly renovated', '+ 555 sq ft', '+ Spacious Kitchen', '+ Multi-Speck Countertops', '+ Breakfast Bar', '+ Nickel Light Fixtures', '+ Hall Bathroom', '+ Walk in Closet in Master', '+ Spacious Living/Dining Areas', '+Fireplace', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES:', '~ Sparkling Blue Pool', '~ Laundry Facility on Site', '~ Friendly and Helpful Staff', '~ Walking distance to Mesa Park', '~ 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Pet Friendly!', 'No Breed Restrictions', 'Pet Refundable Deposit $150', 'Nonrefundable One Time Pet Fee $200', 'Pet Rent $30', 'Sunchase Apartments', '1200 Sunrise Road', 'Round Rock, TX 78664', 'show contact info', 'CALL/TEXT CHRISTA (not a locator)', 'FOR MORE INFO!!!']
